Text: SUIT CAB dP ind - -1.0 to -3.5 inH2O
O2 PRESS IND sw - SURGE TK
ECS RAD TEMP PRIM IN ind - 67 deg-97 degF
ECS RAD TEMP PRIM OUT ind - -20 deg to +63 degF
PRIM GLY EVAP TEMP OUT ind - 35 deg-50.5 degF
PRIM GLY EVAP STM PRESS ind
PRIM GLY DISCH PRESS ind - 40-52 psi
SUIT PRESS ind - = CAB PRESS ind
